title: Glutton Pig - Avoid the vegetables! Eat good stuff

creator: KD Games Studio
descriptionHtml:
A Pig named Gluttie, craving for fast foods but oppressed by surrounding Vigs (yes, the Veggie Pigs!), decides to break the chains and follow the voice of her hearth (or… stomach?)

As she flies to find a better place to live, she has to avoid poisoning vegetables and eat only good stuff.

The more she eats, the bigger she gets – making further progress more challenging. Can you do better than other Glutties from around the world? Don't wait - check it out now!

-------------
